                    .item
                        +img('testi_02.jpg')
                        .text-container
                            p Thank you again and again! I have experienced the fastest support ever. My order arrived on my door step the following day. Your team is always, friendly and very helpful.…
                            strong.h3.text-uppercase DENNIS SIMPSON
